data.description:
Welcome to your new cozy abode nestled in a tranquil 
neighborhood! This charming 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home exudes warmth and comfort, 
offering the perfect retreat from the hustle and bustle of everyday life.
As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious living area highlighted by a beautiful 
woodburning fireplace, perfect for chilly evenings spent curled up with a good book or 
hosting gatherings with loved ones. The newer appliances in the kitchen ensure
convenience and efficiency, making meal preparation a breeze. A recent upgrade includes a brand-new water heater, providing peace of mind and reliability for years to come. Additionally, the new overhead garage door adds both 
functionality and curb appeal to the 1-car attached garage, offering ample space for parking and storage.
With three bedrooms, there's plenty of room for family, guests, or even a home office. Outside, the property boasts a serene ambiance, ideal for enjoying morning coffee on the 
patio or entertaining in the lovely backyard. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this delightful home yours. Schedule a viewing today and experience the comfort and tranquility that awaits you in this desirable neighborhood!
